Short intro to Leon's documentation
===================================

Install Sphinx (http://sphinx.pocoo.org/):

1. Install Python 2.4 or higher (if not already installed)
2. As admin run the following command: easy_install -U Sphinx
3. Make sure you have installed make (xCode on Mac)
4. Done.       


Generating html documentation
-----------------------------

* make html

The output can be found in the _build directory.


Generating pdf documentation
----------------------------

* Install pdflatex (mac: http://www.tug.org/mactex/2011/)
* run: make latexpdf

If you get missing packages errors, install them (as admin) with:
tlmgr install {package name}
